title: Why some analysts think PNoy liable for Mamasapano?
description:
Some experts believe that Pres. Aquino should not turn his back on his liability on the Mamasapano incident. If the basis would be the video showing former Special Action Force (SAF) chief Getulio Napeñas being interrogated by the Cabinet members a day after the Mamasapano encounter.
